/web/20220503085407/https://www.infobae.com/en/2022/03/26/pope-francis-blessed-an-ambulance-that-the-vatican-sent-to-ukraine/}}</ref>，被认为是梵蒂冈一个极不寻常的外交举动<ref>{{Cite web|title=Pope Francis dispatches 2 cardinals to Ukraine|url=https://www.politico.com/news/2022/03/06/pope-francis-dispatches-2-cardinals-to-ukraine-00014429|access-date=2022-04-25|last=Associated Press|first=|work=POLITICO|language=en|archive-date=2022-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220412152842/https://www.politico.com/news/2022/03/06/pope-francis-dispatches-2-cardinals-to-ukraine-00014429}}</ref>。教宗方济各于2022年3月25日为俄罗斯和乌克兰两国举行奉献礼。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Pope consecrates Russia & Ukraine: ‘Spiritual act of trust amid cruel war’ - Vatican News|url=https://www.vaticannews.va/en/pope/news/2022-03/pope-francis-consecration-russia-ukraine-mary-war-lent.html|access-date=2022-04-25|date=2022-03-25|work=www.vaticannews.va|language=en|archive-date=2022-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220326140724/https://www.vaticannews.va/en/pope/news/2022-03/pope-francis-consecration-russia-ukraine-mary-war-lent.html}}</ref>

